    "en": {
      "title": "Killed the three-wheeler driver and stole the cassette",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mount Lavinia CID has arrested a suspect in connection with the abduction and murder of a man in the Thelawala area in Mt.",
        "Police say that he had abducted and killed the driver of the three-wheeler on the 16th to carry out the robbery.",
        "According to the police, the suspect was wanted by the police in connection with a number of crimes such as stealing motorcycles, breaking into houses during the day and stealing property."
      ],
